            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "The vesting period runs from the grant date to the date each tranche vests, and under graded vesting every tranche has its own period. A grant on 1 April 2026 vesting 25 percent a year has vesting periods of one, two, three and four years. The fair value of each tranche is spread over its own period, not over the full four years."
