            "text": "Ind AS 102 treats each tranche of a graded vesting grant as a separate award with its own fair value and its own vesting period, so the total expense is loaded towards earlier years. Under a four year graded grant, year one carries the cost of all four tranches running concurrently, which is materially higher than the equal annual charge a cliff grant would produce."
          }
        }
